  "body": "I guess this is more of a feature request than a bug report, but:\n\nWith 1.3 out, I decided to look into using RBAC, but I found that a pretty significant shortcoming is that I can't specify group membership when using client certs for authn. At least, I'm pretty sure I can't. I just spent a bit looking through the code, as well.\n\nIf the username comes from the CN, then I'd expect the OUs to define group membership, but that seems not to be the case.\n",
